Igennem tiderne har ''The Washington Post'' vundet [[Pulitzerprisen]] 24 gange, i [[2008]] alene seks.<ref>[http://www.nytimes.com/2008/04/07/business/media/07cnd-pulitzers.html?_r=1&hp&oref=slogin Washington Post Wins 6 Pulitzer Prizes – New York Times<!-- Robotgenereret titel -->]</ref> 

